Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:15.06,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, no, what should I do? This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:17.23,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.23,0:00:19.40,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you have time to talk, pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:23.33,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, could someone pick these up too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:26.79,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're all out of order now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.48,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:31.44,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This little idiot is the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:33.44,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:35.82,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:38.35,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong with Aisaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.67,0:00:41.35,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Apparently Taiga loves Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:45.62,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's all into being a "good girl" because Santa's watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:46.96,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:49.98,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Girls love Christmas, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:52.70,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's great to help out with the party preparations,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:54.65,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but are you studying for your exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:55.76,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:58.90,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lately, we've all been getting together and studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:01.82,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, Aisaka-san usually gets good grades,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:04.91,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and Takasu-kun, you have pretty good grades too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:08.67,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But what about Haruta-kun, and Haruta-kun, and Haruta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:10.67,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're worried about Haruta?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:12.97,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And Haruta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:16.53,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haruta-kun's not helping out with the party, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:17.80,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:20.63,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Under Kitamura's orders, Haruta's strictly off limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.63,0:01:22.71,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're having him devote himself to studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:24.48,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If so, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.08,0:01:29.32,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just make sure you two don't let your grades drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.32,0:01:33.23,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It seems like you two are focusing a lot on this party these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:34.65,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm a little worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:36.44,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:39.32,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will you be coming to the party, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:41.05,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like heck!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.05,0:01:45.11,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't have any plans for Christmas Eve, but it's a matter of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:46.91,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:52.93,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hope it's a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:55.91,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone's working so hard for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:01:58.31,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Their efforts have to be rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:34.60,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey! Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:36.22,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minorin! Softball?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:37.31,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:40.02,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We were stretching in the gym just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:41.35,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:43.70,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you don't hurry up, Coach is going to yell at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:46.70,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Got to go, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:49.08,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:52.58,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We keep missing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:54.03,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:55.17,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.42,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Christmas Eve party will definitely be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.44,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you have to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:03.91,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:04.84,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:11.48,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's been acting weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.48,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:16.30,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But if she comes to the party, she'll definitely cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.13,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:18.65,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:21.03,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We need to work hard and make it a fun one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:23.26,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:24.03,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:26.20,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:28.03,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What were you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.04,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We had a little accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.20,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:35.85,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm in the ornament-making group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:38.63,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look, aren't they great?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:43.56,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:46.10,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Clumsy, clumsy! Do it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:47.39,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:49.99,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is it really okay for you to say stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:53.05,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Weren't you trying to be a good girl until Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:56.31,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What an unfortunate slip of the tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:05:00.10,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that going to be used in the party too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:00.40,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:03.43,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To get permission to use the gym,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:07.09,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the teachers made us promise to clean up the storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:08.37,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:14.02,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll do that, so you go over there with Taiga and make stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.46,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here, scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:17.15,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:18.17,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Want to go for it, Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:20.42,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.59,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.71,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't hold the scissors like that, it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:25.42,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.67,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're pretty close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:32.85,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're going to help out over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.83,TD_Main,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:35.39,TD_2nd,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:41.16,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't stir things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.23,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:44.50,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.56,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The fact that Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:51.78,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}L-Likes Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.77,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:58.20,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But lately, everyone's been all about, "Let's get them together!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:01.98,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're worried after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.59,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Could it be jealousy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:06.71,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why the hell would I be jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.09,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:14.96,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't like outsiders interfering in people's love lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.23,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:25.11,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's like a father giving his daughter away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.61,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wouldn’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:30.28,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've never had a daughter nor have I seen my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:34.17,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So she doesn't fall down and gets hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:37.50,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ever so gently, the woman that you've been protecting so tenderly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:39.75,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}gets snatched by some guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:44.38,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't even know if he'll treat her as well as you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.45,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm not thinking anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:48.01,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But it's not very interesting, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:51.61,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seeing Yusaku and Taiga together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.99,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's twisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:55.54,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're not even her father...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:58.13,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But you've decided to never go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.56,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That, and you cherish her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:03.90,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In your heart, you've got a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:08.43,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The three of you know your roles, just like you were playing house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:11.15,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Papa's role, Mama's role, and the child's role?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:13.09,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the hell are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:19.48,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you playing Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:23.19,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your relationship with Taiga is really unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:26.53,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You should quit playing house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:33.07,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You probably got it wrong from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:36.05,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You should open your eyes before you really get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:39.39,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just scratch it all out, and start from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.10,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:47.07,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Include me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:48.61,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}From the beginning too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:49.99,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:53.07,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:55.00,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay if you didn't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:59.45,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:01.41,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Forget everything I said just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:03.92,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:08.05,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The person you understand the least is yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:29.02,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.32,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please put your pencils down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:34.81,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haruta, you're too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:37.42,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Quiet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:39.97,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You still have class tomorrow and the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:42.54,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So don't let Christmas get to your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:45.63,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:48.47,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Want to eat lunch with Ryuji and me on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:51.38,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry, I've got practice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:52.81,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:54.01,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minorin says she's got softball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:57.59,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I got it, I heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:59.11,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry, I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:01.38,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though you took the time to invite me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:04.43,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:10.46,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It just seems like you don't have much time to talk lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:12.02,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You and Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:16.12,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, Coach has completely fallen to the Dark Side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.78,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Practice is really tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.37,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:20.91,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:25.45,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She ran away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:26.46,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:31.21,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was thinking I'd give you two some time alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.26,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When we arrive at the restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:36.68,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd say, "Oh! I forgot I have something to do!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:39.48,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You even came up with that lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.72,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Angel Taiga-sama is really into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:45.26,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, what can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:46.83,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There'll be other chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:49.02,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's get something to eat on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.47,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.67,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It wasn't a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:53.32,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I really have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.04,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What sort of something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:57.18,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I need go to the post office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.90,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've got to go home first to pick up the stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:00.95,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:02.90,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't have to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:02.90,TD_2nd,Kiyohara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:03.62,TD_Main,Kiyohara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.74,TD_Main,Kiyohara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, hey, are you free?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:06.84,TD_Main,Kiyohara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:08.08,TD_Main,Kiyohara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've got something to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:10.42,TD_Main,Kiyohara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How about lunch with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:11.71,TD_Main,Kiyohara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:13.05,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.02,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've got plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:19.13,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have to go with her to the post office.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:20.45,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey! Ryuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:22.22,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I said you don't have to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:24.01,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nevermind that, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.94,TD_Main,Kiyohara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, wait, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:35.19,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's with you? Lying like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:40.47,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Besides, why are you so friendly with a girl who's been hanging all over Kitamura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:42.27,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scratch that. Rephrase...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:44.18,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The very nice Kiharu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.38,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nevermind, let's go to the post office.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:48.36,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I go, then it won't be a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:50.37,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And, the stuff is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:52.97,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:55.67,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Were you going to take all of this by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:57.09,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't touch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:11:00.13,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's fine, you go over there and bring the cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:02.13,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:04.39,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:09.10,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If it weren't Christmas, I would have punched you for looking without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:12.15,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But good girl me will forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:15.69,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}These are Christmas presents I'm sending to my parents{' house}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:17.36,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:21.38,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're not thinking about starting over or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:22.32,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.37,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because it's Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.80,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because they're my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:27.54,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.29,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was trying to keep it a secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:33.37,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I have presents for you and Yacchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:35.25,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's not what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:37.84,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:40.97,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But right now, I don't want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:43.32,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll go get the cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.73,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:50.89,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Santa Claus?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:59.00,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I went to an all-girls Catholic school ever since elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.78,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I couldn't get into the high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:03.66,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because I was pretty bad in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.62,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At that school, one of the things they did was volunteer work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:10.11,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}With the sisters, well, basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:12.39,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hate saying it like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:15.45,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We taught games to disadvantaged children...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:17.67,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And helped them with various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:20.88,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The boxes from Santa are for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:25.22,TD_FB,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}First it's your parents, now it's disadvantaged kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:29.18,TD_FB,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry, but I don't get what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:32.60,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to tell them, "Someone is watching."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.48,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Christmas is a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:39.55,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if you don't have parents to raise you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:43.21,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if you can't believe in God...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:45.63,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even so, someone is watching you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:47.03,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's what I want to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:51.75,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Somewhere, there is really someone out there who notices them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:52.84,TD_FB,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That sort of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:54.00,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.11,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:56.29,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's just self-satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:59.60,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But that's what I want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:03.51,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Somewhere, someone is watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:06.49,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In my case, Santa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:08.07,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Santa, Santa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:10.01,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You really believe in him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:14.18,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I really love Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.03,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everywhere you look...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:18.48,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The town, the stores, everywhere is sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.89,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bright, beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.06,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone looks like they're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:27.86,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It feels like happiness is just flowing from every corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:31.45,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think to myself, "If I could become part of that..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.96,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By being a good girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:36.91,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to become part of that happy scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:41.63,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To be one of the happy faces in a Christmas town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:45.38,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:48.18,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've really met Santa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:51.89,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When I was little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:54.89,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Papa and Mama were still at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.65,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}On the night before Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:59.52,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was sleeping under the tree in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.99,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I woke up when I got cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:03.48,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then I looked outside the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:07.60,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Santa was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:13.33,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Santa gave me a present and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:17.47,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Taiga, if you're a good girl, I'll come and see you again."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.49,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1} Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:22.08,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe it was all just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:23.87,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:26.17,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was a really happy dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:30.56,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why I want to be a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:34.49,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Am I being dumb for believing a dream like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:37.23,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:38.78,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:40.34,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:42.08,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:46.53,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not like I'm clinging to someone who really exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:52.57,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Keep going, okay, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.33,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:55.60,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.50,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Christmas tree has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:02.38,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:06.10,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When we put it together, it'll definitely be amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:09.72,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It looks like it'll be a great party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.05,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuri-chan, why don't you come too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:13.08,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As I said, like heck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:14.67,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a matter of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:16.73,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, that reminds me. I should buy myself a treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:18.65,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like a watch or a bag or some accessories...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.43,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A treat for working hard for thirty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:22.22,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:23.97,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I bet you just think it's a waste a money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:27.59,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I bet you think, "a treat for yourself," is just a marketing trick for single women, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:27.59,TD_2nd,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:31.02,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They say that you need 70 million yen to retire, but this is no time to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:34.51,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But you know, if you hold back on everything you want, and at the end you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:36.53,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"I did it! I've saved up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:39.93,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you going to do with that high powered hybrid car you bought if the world turns to a place where you can't use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:40.96,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:44.54,TD_Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe I should buy a condo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:48.36,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's here, it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:50.34,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are all the parts here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:52.74,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How did you get something this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:55.80,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was the decoration at this modeling event I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.46,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I got them to give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:15:58.72,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:01.09,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you get my awesomeness?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:03.18,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah! Despite being a Stupid Chihuahua, this is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:05.61,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is a great tree, I've got to give you that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:09.11,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll be even greater after it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:10.37,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:11.78,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Full power into assembly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:14.57,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are these the right parts for the legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.57,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wow, I'm so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:17.33,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:18.55,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:19.70,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't that for the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:21.37,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:26.32,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You seem pretty light, could you get on my back and attach this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:28.54,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}With the shoes I wore to the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:30.68,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To each their own, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.54,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, please take them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:34.43,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Ryuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.16,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:37.43,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You help out too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.40,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is probably next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:44.39,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey! What are you doing? That was dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:46.32,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you doing, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:48.05,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're really athletic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.96,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just what you'd expect from Tenori Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:55.07,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But that's what I want to believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:58.27,TD_FB,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Somewhere, someone is watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:16:59.99,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.69,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:07.35,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe there wasn't someone who was watching you these past seventeen years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.61,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But now it's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:12.55,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:14.51,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:18.73,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yasuko-chan and myself... Even Inko-chan's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:23.14,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When tomorrow comes, I'm sure Kushieda too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:25.84,TD_FB,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Their efforts have to be rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:26.39,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:28.64,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They have to be rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:31.94,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone is going to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.85,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone is going to be rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:37.14,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:39.01,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:40.87,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:43.12,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I brought this from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.12,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Put this on the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:46.62,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you sure? Something this pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.51,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It looks kinda expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:49.96,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.60,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's my favorite ornament.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:56.14,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But it's too big, so I can't put it on the tree in my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:57.59,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:00.30,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then I'll put it on carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:05.77,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Curtains closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:07.73,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's plugged in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:09.60,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:11.65,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(0,100)}I'm going to turn off the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:22.99,TD_Main,Boys,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.41,TD_Main,Kihara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:26.25,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:27.50,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:54.55,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.61,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Was anyone hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:15.30,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minorin, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.72,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.25,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You couldn't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:19.80,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:22.49,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:24.14,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:26.94,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This was just an unlucky accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:26.94,TD_2nd,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.02,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:32.11,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think it was because I was spacing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:34.02,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hitting the ball like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.07,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}On top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:38.30,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Breaking something so important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:40.68,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:43.33,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It probably won't be like it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:45.39,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But please let me do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:51.75,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then, Ryuji will help...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:51.75,TD_2nd,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:54.54,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, please stop! Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:56.54,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minorin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:06.30,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun, please, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:09.69,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please let me work on this by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:14.20,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:16.49,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:18.21,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This kind of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:20.74,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Having you help me like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:21.83,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:22.95,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:25.51,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You do what you have to do for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:27.95,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't be helping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.11,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be doing it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:40.76,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:41.88,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.32,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:45.68,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:47.36,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:50.72,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.10,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.21,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:57.64,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:59.71,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What was broken can be fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:00.94,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:04.28,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It won't be like it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:06.68,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, it's still sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:10.34,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know whether it can be fixed or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:11.30,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:13.55,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:14.58,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll be fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:16.27,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However many times it breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:21.00,TD_Main,Minori/team,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:23.59,TD_Main,Minori/team,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We are truly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:28.89,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks, Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:33.06,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's even cuter than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:37.44,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:40.60,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come tomorrow, to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:42.40,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll definitely be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.78,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to spend it with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:48.46,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:49.55,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:52.70,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I caused all this trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:55.12,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:56.08,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:57.50,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:00.48,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.86,0:22:05.38,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.71,0:22:07.23,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:28.30,TD_Main,Boys,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Christmas Eve, Christmas Eve, Christmas Eve, Christmas Eve!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:29.90,TD_Main,Boys,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's Christmas Eve party time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:31.87,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want another cup of fruit punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:35.03,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? Where did Taiga go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.77,TD_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}
